Ranger Help for: meditation
============================

SYNTAX:      meditate
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   3
BASE SP:     NA
SKILL TYPE:  religious

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to enter a meditative state, communing with
nature to restore spell points. The Ranger must not be in combat to
meditate. The amount of spell points restored depends on the Ranger's
wisdom, guild level, and the terrain they are in. Meditating in the
Ranger's primary terrain is more effective. This is the primary way
Rangers recover their spell points in the field.
